OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775523444
OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap ends and state
OL,4,Cpensions rise starting today
OL,6,FBenefits and pensions rise today as
OL,7,Fgovernment policy changes aimed at
OL,8,Feasing the cost of living come into
OL,9,Feffect.
OL,11,FThe two-child benefit cap ended on
OL,12,FMonday, in a move expected to lift
OL,13,F450,000 children out of poverty.
OL,15,FFirst introduced by the Conservatives
OL,16,Fin 2017, the cap limited households to
OL,17,Fonly receiving per-child financial
OL,18,Fsupport for their first two children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
