OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775523444
OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap ends and state
OL,4,Cpensions rise starting today
OL,6,FThe biggest rise will be for those who
OL,7,Fbecame state pension age after April
OL,8,F2016, who will see their flat-rate
OL,9,Fstate pension increase to #241.30 a
OL,10,Fweek, giving them #12,547.60 a year.
OL,12,FThose who reached state pension age
OL,13,Fbefore April 2016 will see their state
OL,14,Fpensions increase to #184.90 a week,
OL,15,For #9,614.80 a year - giving them an
OL,16,Fextra #439.40.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
