OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775523444
OL,3,CTwo-child benefit cap ends and state
OL,4,Cpensions rise starting today
OL,6,F"We are working closely with
OL,7,Finternational partners to push for a
OL,8,Fde-escalation in the Middle East and
OL,9,Fthe re-opening of the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz," Starmer said.
OL,12,F"This is the most effective way to
OL,13,Fease the pressure on the cost of
OL,14,Fliving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
